In order to participate, just do the review then send me a link on Telegram: @Woshib  Week 1 - 27/09 to 3/09 Week 2 - 4/09 to 10/09 Week 3 - 11/09 to 17/09 ... Bounty pool: 6,600,00 GYM -  approx. 2,000,000$  The program will run until the end of token sale. The bounties will be paid after token sale end.   General Bounty distribution:   Please check your participation in this spreadsheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12seFDHOkSVTqNyfg7aLWCLKYUb6ax7t3eNYLa4R6u2k/edit?usp=sharing   All participants are required to join GYM Ledger's telegram group: https://t.me/gymrewards   Please note: You must provide an ETH address that you own private keys, not an exchange address!   Needless to say, as in any other token sale or ICO, keep your account safe and use a secure password.     Stakes will be paid depending on followers (at the start of the campaign).  250-749 followers:   1 stake per tweet or retweet 750-1499 followers:   2 stakes per tweet or retweet 1500-9999 followers:   4 stakes per tweet or retweet 10.000+ followers:   6 stakes per tweet or retweet  Minimum 3 tweets or retweets per week Maximum 2 tweets or retweets per day, and 10 retweets per week  Application: 1. Participants are required to keep the local thread and Telegram groups alive by posting and translating regular updates, news or any important announcements. A single post thread will be rejected. 2. Automatic (Google or similar) translations or translations with low quality will be rejected. 3. Unnecessary or repeated posts shall be rejected for stake counting 4.
